Down arrow icon












The Office of the Dean of Students
The Office of the Dean of Students strives to be the campus leader in fostering a caring and supportive environment where all students matter. Through a variety of offices, including Student Assistance, Community Standards, Student Legal, and Student Veterans, we assist students in resolving issues so that they can focus on their academic and social development.
WE'RE HERE TO HELP.





